{"about_the_game":"<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1563730/extras/WH_01.png?t=1725324296\" /><br>Every small town has its secrets, but some are worse than others...<br><br><strong>Witching Hour</strong> is a horror story that takes you out of your family home and across <i>Hollow Hills</i> to face its dark history of witchcraft. Your fate depends on making difficult choices, your relationship with your father and sister, and confrontations with the matriarch of the town\u2019s affliction, <i>Lucilia</i>.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1563730/extras/WH_02.png?t=1725324296\" /><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>As Above, So Below</strong>: Learn of the \u201cother church\u201d in town, with its members and location hidden to most locals.<br></li><li><strong>Hollow Hills</strong>: Explore locations like <i>The Pasture</i>, <i>The Parish</i>, <i>Eastern Village</i>, <i>Greenwater Gardens</i>, and more.<br></li><li><strong>Witching Hour</strong>: There\u2019s no place like home, but be cautious to not wander your family house too much at night.</li></ul><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1563730/extras/WitchingHour_map.png?t=1725324296\" /><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1563730/extras/WH_03.png?t=1725324296\" /><br><strong>Explore, discover, and survive:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Explore a variety of grim locations with hidden clues and cryptic puzzles.<br></li><li>Engage in frightening encounters with the witch Lucilia and her coven.<br></li><li>Learn of <i>black magick</i> and <i>witchcraft</i> while the world starts to break around you.<br></li><li>A cast of talented voice actors bring the dialogue and characters to life.</li></ul><br><strong>Genre:</strong> Story-driven psychological horror